{"tid":1528080,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗仔好似好難呼吸","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:11.000Z","uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"928a49ab2ec3ba0316568a21d114351c1e1470ba","tid":1528080,"uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"新手琴日領養咗隻貴婦狗返屋企，發現佢一興奮就好似人咁扯哮咁咳，有時仲有合埋口咳咳咳，好似咳緊啲野出黎咁，當舊野咳咗出黎佢又會吞返落去...<br />\n今日帶咗佢去睇醫生，醫生話佢心臟冇問題，冇生命危險，咁我都暫時安心啲，之後醫生話通常啲細狗仔氣窄都會有咁嘅情況...<br />\n<br />\n但我都係有啲擔心，大家嘅狗仔有冇試過有呢啲情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我比佢食多幾日醫生開嘅藥睇下點就會再帶佢去另一間獸醫再睇多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8555a42f29d033fd44c783e5852ed229c0893ee","tid":1528080,"uid":259345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db121fcbab2a83c1215e1da11118a82cabce1b48","tid":1528080,"uid":283431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:57:22.000Z","msg":"我個fd隻poodle都係咁 似咳又似喘氣 好似喉嚨卡住啲嘢咁 不過冇咳過嘢出嚟 我都聽過幾多poodle有呢個問題"},{"pid":"0bccd5971d1a82dca01aeeda6befce3e270e8f4e","tid":1528080,"uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db121fcbab2a83c1215e1da11118a82cabce1b48","tid":1528080,"uid":283431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:57:22.000Z","msg":"我個fd隻poodle都係咁 似咳又似喘氣 好似喉嚨卡住啲嘢咁 不過冇咳過嘢出嚟 我都聽過幾多poodle有呢個問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"係啊！！咁係咪即係正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好擔心係卡住啲野/呼吸唔到"},{"pid":"d32dff8